WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.521 --> 00:00:14.796
Hi!  Welcome to Rosie's Place!

00:00:15.186 --> 00:00:17.186
I'm Rosie!

00:00:17.725 --> 00:00:18.683
[beep, beep]

00:00:18.842 --> 00:00:21.304
Ooooo.... the mailman's here!

00:00:34.085 --> 00:00:35.985
I got mail!

00:00:38.310 --> 00:00:42.283
It says: To Rosie From Fuzzles.

00:00:45.770 --> 00:00:48.451
It's an invitation.

00:00:50.235 --> 00:01:00.002
Dear Rosie.  You are invited to my tea party today.

00:01:00.400 --> 00:01:02.700
Love, Fuzzles.

00:01:04.020 --> 00:01:08.366
Wear your favourite dress.

00:01:08.780 --> 00:01:13.100
I love dressing up!  Let's go to my boutique!

00:01:14.658 --> 00:01:45.260
[music]

00:01:46.100 --> 00:01:48.100
I'm over here.

00:01:49.340 --> 00:01:50.550
Hee hee hee

00:01:51.980 --> 00:01:54.300
SURPRISE!  I'm right here!

00:01:54.966 --> 00:01:57.120
Welcome to my boutique!

00:01:57.458 --> 00:02:00.410
There are so many beautiful dresses.

00:02:01.226 --> 00:02:03.200
I like this one.

00:02:03.244 --> 00:02:07.370
Look at the colour.  It's so beautiful.  Isn't it?

00:02:07.726 --> 00:02:10.370
Look at this beautiful dress...

00:02:10.457 --> 00:02:13.620
it has a beautiful bow.

00:02:13.975 --> 00:02:15.980
And it's so red.

00:02:16.775 --> 00:02:18.320
Ooooo...Look at this one!

00:02:18.697 --> 00:02:21.450
It's so shimmery and shiny!

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:25.890
Ooooo... I like this one.  Look at all the roses.

00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:29.370
Oh... and I like this one!  It's so...

00:02:30.033 --> 00:02:32.520
beautiful and perfect!

00:02:33.400 --> 00:02:35.850
I know. It's so hard to choose.

00:02:36.283 --> 00:02:38.280
They're all so beautiful.

00:02:38.657 --> 00:02:41.620
How 'bout I try them all on?

00:02:42.050 --> 00:02:42.820
Ahhh!

00:02:43.067 --> 00:02:45.760
And we'll have a fashion show!

00:02:46.169 --> 00:02:49.520
And you tell me which one you like the most!

00:03:03.415 --> 00:03:06.800
Click here to go to the fashion show.

